title: 12/23/20 DPS - BEST OF
itunes:title: 12/23/20 DPS - BEST OF
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP recaps last night's Warriors/Nets and Clippers/Lakers games with ESPN's Frank Isola. What questions did Brooklyn answer last night? We're also joined by former NFL Defensive Lineman and ESPN Analyst Booger McFarland. What would he do if he were the Jets GM. And it's that time of year again, Fritzy makes his triumphant return with Holiday names. Merry Christmas and Happy Holidays to all!
